benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: POST /1.0/kb/admin/invoices - Trigger an invoice generation for all parked accounts

covered: Valid Payload: Scenarios cover successful invoice generation with valid parameters.
Invalid Payload: Scenarios test various invalid inputs, including missing headers and invalid parameter values.
Empty Response: Scenario for no parked accounts ensures the system handles empty data responses.
Authorization: Scenarios cover unauthorized access with invalid tokens.
Server Error Handling: Scenarios test server unavailability and transient network failures.
gaps: Duplicate Submission: No tests cover how the system handles duplicate submissions of the same request.
Large Payloads: No tests specifically address handling of very large payloads beyond the maximum limit.
Concurrency Issues: No tests for race conditions when multiple administrators send concurrent requests.
recommendations: Add tests for duplicate submissions to ensure the system handles them gracefully.
Include scenarios for handling very large payloads to test system limits.
Add tests for concurrency issues to ensure correct processing of simultaneous requests.
